PrecisAmendment to the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS -- NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR NON-COMPULSORY AREAS raising the charges for the services of a pilot through the non-compulsory pilotage waters of Newfoundland and Labrador by 3%, followed by a further increase of 3% to be effective one year after the first comes into effect.
